Package com.quantimodo.tools

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    QApplication
    Should provide dependencies and EventBus for other components of quantimodo-tools For example implementations see QBaseApplication
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    QBaseApplication
    Base implementation of QApplication interface which provides ObjectGraph and EventBus
    QTools
    Enter point of QuantimodoTools Used to get instance of application, in order to use tools components QTools.init(QApplication) should be called , with instance of QApplication
    ToolsPrefs
    Configuration of toolprefs and quantimodo app
    UserPreferences
    Class to manage the user data like name, id, and others
